### 🔐 Backend Features Implemented
- **Secure Login System**  
  - Staff enter Hospital Name, Post, ID, and Password.  
  - Credentials verified against a **blockchain smart contract**.  
  - On success → JWT token issued + “Verified on Blockchain” badge.  
  - On failure (3 wrong attempts) → account locked for 15 minutes, activity logged.  

- **Role-Based Access Control**  
  - **Admin**: Full audit table (logins, record access, IP, blockchain hash), anomaly alerts, locked accounts management.  
  - **Doctor**: Assigned patient records, every access logged to blockchain.  
  - **Nurse**: Ward patient list only.  
  - **Pharmacist**: Pending prescriptions.  
  - **Receptionist**: Appointment scheduling.  

- **Audit & Monitoring**  
  - Every action (login, record access, logout, timeout) permanently recorded on blockchain.  
  - Admin dashboard shows real-time anomaly detection (e.g., too many records accessed quickly).  

- **Session Management**  
  - 9‑minute inactivity warning popup.  
  - Auto logout at 10 minutes, logged in audit trail.  

